Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.31,0:00:14.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,实现自己的愿望更好的办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.39,0:00:21.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想消除这肉眼所看不见的烧伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.84,0:00:24.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,只需接受那圣痕便行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.88,0:00:25.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:28.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你作为被选中的Master
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:31.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,有无为此圣杯战争而战斗的意向
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:33.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.34,0:01:00.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好  大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.75,0:01:02.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,这样见面已经是第二次了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.14,0:01:05.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不好  这家伙和我们不是一个层次的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.13,0:01:08.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面  凛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.68,0:01:12.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我是伊利雅  伊利雅斯菲尔·冯·阿因兹贝伦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.68,0:01:12.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs16\fnsimhei}Illyasviel·Von·Einzbern
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:14.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,这样说该明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.11,0:01:16.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,阿因兹贝伦…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.28,0:01:19.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,打招呼到此为止就可以了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:21.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你们都会死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.24,0:01:24.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  杀掉你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.04,0:01:26.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉他们  Berserker
