Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.02,0:03:27.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉他们  干掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:56.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:03:59.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker  就在那里哦
