Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:55.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,根本没可能打赢嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:57.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我的Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:00.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,是希腊最强的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.91,0:06:02.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,希腊最强的英雄…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:04.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:07.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,没错哦  在这里的就是名为赫拉克勒斯的魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:07.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}赫拉克勒斯：希腊最伟大的英雄,曾立下十二件功勋（十二试炼）,死后成神。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:10.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,赫拉克勒斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:15.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  是跟你们这种程度所役使的英雄有天壤之别
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:17.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,最强的怪物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:21.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:25.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,从头部开始砍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:23.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那家伙还会再生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.03,0:06:36.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.39,0:06:43.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我…  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:50.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:11.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:13.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:17.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.33,0:07:30.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  这样真有够无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:31.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:39.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:42.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再见面的时候会杀掉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:01.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在想些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:04.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  已经没办法再救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:22.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候  我曾经很憧憬正义的伙伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:25.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那是为什么啊  曾经很憧憬？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:27.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,已经放弃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:29.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  非常可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:31.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄是有保质期的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:35.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,长大成人以后就很难这样自称了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:41.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情  再早一些察觉到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:47.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
