Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:52.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  真的是没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.58,0:08:54.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:57.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因为没办法  所以由我来代替你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:09:00.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然老爸已经是成人没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:02.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,但我的话一定没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:11.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧  我一定会好好把老爸的梦想实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:14.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:45.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:09:59.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:05.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚…  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:11.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:14.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我擅自泡了茶  卫宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:19.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,为  为什么你会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:24.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来连像样点的茶叶都没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:28.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,泡茶的袋子至少也准备个三角形的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:31.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,远坂  你为什么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:32.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:36.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前  应该先谢谢我把你搬到这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:39.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,搬到这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.51,0:10:48.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:55.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  我被那个怪物…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.73,0:10:59.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  为什么我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:12.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  为什么我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:15.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之后你的伤自动愈合了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:16.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,自己愈合是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:20.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,从我看来Saber好像也有自我治疗的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:23.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,所以可能是那能力流到你身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:32.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,由Sevent给Master提供魔力什么的本来是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:35.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  你也是个出人意料的Master
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.60,0:11:37.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:41.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,想要去救Servant的Master真是闻所未闻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:45.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你死了的话Saber也就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.88,0:11:50.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫同学  接下来你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.87,0:11:58.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是不想重蹈十年前的覆辙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:03.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,对圣杯那种东西没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:05.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道你会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:09.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊  说那种话会被Saber杀掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.47,0:12:11.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,被Saber…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:15.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为Servant会无条件地服从人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:19.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,把圣杯拿到手就能实现愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.43,0:12:23.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,这对于身为守护者的Servant也不例外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:26.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,他们之所以回应Master的召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:28.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了能拿到圣杯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:31.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,实现自己各种各样的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.42,0:12:34.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,为了圣杯Saber会…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:42.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,但是Saber是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:43.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚还流了那么多的血
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.30,0:12:46.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,对Servant而言是没有生死的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:49.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,即使丧命也只是回到原本的地方而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:51.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因此而互相残杀什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:54.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如果就这样放着别的Master不管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:56.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,无辜的人就会死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:01.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,Servant的燃料是魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:04.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,积蓄的魔力越是多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:07.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就越能自由使用生前的特殊能力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:09.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:12.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他们是灵体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:15.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,吃掉灵魂的话就能获得营养
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.53,0:13:19.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说也有为了补充魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:23.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,而指使Servant袭击人类并吃掉其灵魂的Master
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:26.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,Servant会吃人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:35.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…不对  Saber是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.61,0:13:40.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:44.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,无论其他的Master做什么你都袖手旁观吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:45.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话只有阻止他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:47.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,真是败给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:49.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你说自己不会去打倒其他Master
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:52.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,可是当他做坏事的时候却又要去打倒他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:58.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道你自己是矛盾的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:02.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道这样很自私
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:05.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,但我想不到其他的行动方针
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:12.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一个问题  可以说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:14.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.11,0:14:18.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚的Master肯定会来杀我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:23.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子的Servant层次和我们不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:25.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去可以说是坐以待毙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:29.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你连自己都无法保护吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:34.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那个Servant是叫赫拉克勒斯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:37.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,真是被藐视得可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:39.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄的真名被知道了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.70,0:14:41.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,就等于是把自己的弱点暴露给敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:44.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  Saber的真名是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.43,0:14:47.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是不要知道的比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.08,0:14:50.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你对别人  口风好像不是很紧的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:53.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,别人  是指远坂你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:56.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不记得和你是自己人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:15:00.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不用送我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:03.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,把我搬回家的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.89,0:15:08.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,忘记说了  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.51,0:15:21.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,今后别把我当成人类看待会比较轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.31,0:15:32.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,圣杯战争
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:36.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦参加就必须打倒所有的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:42.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,为了打倒对手  甚至去加害毫无关系的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.24,0:15:45.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不做点什么的话  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:47.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,庆幸吧  少年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:52.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你终于可以如愿以偿了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:10.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不对  我想拯救别人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:13.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不想让任何人死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:15.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎  退后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.07,0:16:20.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber一心想要保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:24.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,都成那样子了还…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:27.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  Saber呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:37.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  樱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.77,0:16:40.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  为什么这个时候会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:43.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是早睡早起的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:45.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:52.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我在散步啊  散步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:53.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那么再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:17:00.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,血的…味道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:07.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.85,0:17:10.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,藤村老师  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:13.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,真是令人清爽的早晨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:16.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,这种日子真想去吃点麦芽饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:19.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得有做好海味小菜放在家里的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:21.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,海味小菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:25.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还浓厚多汁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:27.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,好  从早上开始就情绪高涨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:29.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,记得帮我多留几碗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:39.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,几乎已经找遍整个屋子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.13,0:17:43.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:48.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:33.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:36.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚才…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:41.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,脸色不太好的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:46.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不  已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:48.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:52.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  士郎  关于昨晚的事我有话想和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.31,0:18:53.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:57.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,Master有着那样的行为会让我很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:01.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗是我的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:04.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎请做好自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:07.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,作为Master的你没有保护我的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:09.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有理由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:13.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,救女孩子还需要理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:18.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,再问一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.75,0:19:21.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,叫你Saber可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:24.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  既然作为Servant和你订立契约之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:26.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是士郎的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:30.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那是为了赢得圣杯战争吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.34,0:19:33.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:35.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:39.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,但是Saber  你跟着我胜算很小哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:42.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,这是说你没有战斗的意向吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:44.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗的意向是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:47.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  无论结果如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:49.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是我决定的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:50.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:53.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,只是没有胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.74,0:19:56.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有胜算的话  就由我来创造
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:19:59.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,用有可能的所有方法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:04.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,难道  为了得到力量而袭击人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.46,0:20:07.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,这是没可能会使用的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:10.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,伤害手无寸铁的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:13.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,有违骑士道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:28.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  如果是Master的命令就只有遵从
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:33.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候作为践踏我尊严的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.93,0:20:36.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,就是必须要使用一个刻印
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:39.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我绝不让那种事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:43.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:48.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,在不知不觉中侮辱了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.71,0:20:50.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不  请抬起头来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.07,0:20:53.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是不知道士郎的意图
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:55.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,就妄自猜测了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:04.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然全是些不明白的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.40,0:21:08.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,但也只能凭借在我们能力范围以内的行动去解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:11.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:13.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.78,0:21:18.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,空腹是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:20.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,去吃饭吧  士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:33.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:37.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  你早上习惯吃和食吗
